    Conditions
  - Invocation=The Universal Elixir
Format: verse
---
Nature willingly receiveth honor and reverence.
Grace faithfully attributeth all honor and glory unto God.
Nature feareth shame and contempt.
Grace rejoiceth to suffer reproach for the Name of Jesus.
